                                <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
                        unser <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist on geverde.
                                <expan>Getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir ewch, daz ir <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> mit <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gerichte<ex>n</ex></expan> unbeswert lasset und niht umbtreibet. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb
                        ewch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schulden</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
